item.title: CVE-2022-22486|2024-08-03T03:14:55.255Z -- ibm -- tivoli%20workload%20scheduler
item.description: IBM Tivoli Workload Scheduler 9.4, 9.5, and 10.1 is vulnerable to an XML External Entity Injection (XXE) attack when processing XML data. A remote attacker could exploit this vulnerability to expose sensitive information or consume memory resources. IBM X-Force ID: 226328.
